---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="周度复盘 | 1H币研" description="每周比特币 & 以太坊价格行为复盘，基于 Al Brooks 方法论的周度技术分析总结。" lang="zh" activeNav="weekly">
<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "周度复盘",
  "description": "每周比特币 & 以太坊价格行为复盘，基于 Al Brooks 方法论的周度技术分析总结。",
  "inLanguage": "zh-CN",
  "datePublished": "2026-01-05T08:00:00+08:00",
  "dateModified": new Date().toISOString(),
  "author": {
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "1H Crypto Trader"
  },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "1H币研",
    "logo": {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "url": "https://1hcrypto.com/favicon.svg"
    }
  },
  "mainEntityOfPage": {
    "@type": "@id",
    "@id": "https://1hcrypto.com/zh/weekly/"
  }
})}</script>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">周度复盘</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] text-sm">每周日发布 · 基于 <span class="text-primary">Al Brooks 价格行为学</span> 的 BTC & ETH 周度技术分析</p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-[var(--border)]">每周日 20:00 更新</span>
      <span>|</span>
      <span>交易日历：周一至周五</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 最新周度复盘 -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">最新复盘</h2>
      <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] ml-2">2026-05-25 ~ 2026-05-31</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20">BTC/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 border border-purple-500/20">ETH/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">周度</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">BTC 周度复盘：突破在即，等待确认</h3>

      <!-- 本周关键数据 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">本周开盘</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">$71,200</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">本周收盘</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">$73,850</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">周度振幅</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">3.7%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">模拟盘 P&L</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">+$4,200</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 周度分析 -->
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-white">周线结构：</strong>本周 BTC 周线收阳，收盘价站上 EMA20（$72,500）。连续三周低点抬高（Higher Low），结构偏多。周线级别需求区 $70,000–$71,000 守住，为多头提供支撑。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Al Brooks 信号：</strong>本周 1H 图出现两次看涨 Engulfing Bar（周二亚洲盘、周四伦敦盘），且收盘均突破前一根 K 线高点，符合 Al Brooks 的「趋势 bar」定义。周五纽约盘出现小幅回调，但未跌破 EMA20，属于健康的回踩确认。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">ETH/BTC 比率：</strong>本周 ETH 表现强于 BTC，ETH/BTC 比率从 0.048 升至 0.051。山寨季预期升温，资金有轮动迹象。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">下周关键位：</strong>阻力 $75,000（周线前高）· 支撑 $72,500（EMA20）/ $71,000（周度需求区）。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 关联交易记录 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2">关联交易记录</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <a href="/zh/trading/" class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-colors no-underline">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">多单</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white">BTC/USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">5/28 入场 · 已止盈 →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/zh/daily/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-primary hover:underline">查看本周每日研判 →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 历史周度复盘列表 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--border)]"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">历史复盘</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-05-19 ~ 2026-05-24 周度复盘</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 震荡蓄力 · EMA20 支撑有效 · 模拟盘 +$2,800</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-05-12 ~ 2026-05-17 周度复盘</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 突破 $70,000 · 周线阳线确认 · 模拟盘 +$5,100</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-05-05 ~ 2026-05-10 周度复盘</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 回踩 $68,000 支撑 · 看跌 Pin Bar 失效 · 模拟盘 +$1,400</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 周度方法论说明 -->
  <div class="card p-6 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[var(--border)]">
    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-3">周度复盘方法论</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>基于 Al Brooks 价格行为学，聚焦 1H/4H K 线结构</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>每周汇总模拟盘交易记录，P&L 透明展示</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>结合链上数据（交易所净流出/流入）辅助判断</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>下周操作计划：关键位 + 触发条件 + 风险管理</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
